  <p>"Drawing" is a basic drawing application for the GNOME desktop.</p>
  <p>You can edit or create pictures (PNG, JPEG or BMP) using tools, which can
  be chosen in the side pane. More options are available in the bottom bar,
  such as the tool size and color.</p>
  <p>The window's subtitle should provide useful informations about how to use
  the active tool.</p>

